The gas valve train helps ensure the boiler
operates safely by starting or stopping the

19
00:01:05,370 --> 00:01:07,479
fuel flow into the
system.

20
00:01:07,479 --> 00:01:11,000
It both monitors and regulates fuel pressure
within the system.

21
